@Macmac1969 Hello Steve,
In order to best assist you with your request, can you please indicate the reference number of your file by private message on Messenger https://t.co/OiVO5iclp4
Thank you

@NyirendaR Hi Richard, once you have made your declaration online, you can follow the progress of your luggage here: https://t.co/fi40kXJSeY
We are still available in private messaging (TW/FB)
Have a nice day, Yvonne

@FTVBrandon Dear Brandon, we are sincerely sorry for the inconvenience of contacting us at this time.
We invite you to DM us with all the details of your reservation and your request which will allow us to meet your expectations as well as possible  
Have a good day, Yvonne

@DavidoggyHogg Hello David, our customer service on Messenger has taken your request into account. Unfortunately we cannot guarantee an immediate response but our team will do their best.
We are sincerely sorry and apologise. 
Regards Yvonne

@Lord_Hillier Dear Lord, we apologise for the circumstances.
In order to assist you in the best possible way, can you please indicate the reference number of your file by private message on Messenger (for Facebook) or by DM (on Twitter)? 
Thank you, Yvonne

@savthecupcake Dear Savannah, we invite you to consult the ongoing information of your file on the page: https://t.co/T3aL4R5RVW
Thank you for your understanding.
Yvonne

@arrancosything Hi @arrancosything, we understand your disappointment. We will come back to you in private message to inform you about the progress of your request. 
Thank you for your understanding. 
Have a good day, Yvonne

@unapologetic_mf Hello @unapologetic_mf, we regret this incident at the arrival of your flight. Did you make your loss report online to locate your luggage?
We remain at your disposal.
Good day, Yvonne

@beckswatson86 Hello @beckswatson86, we are sincerely sorry for the inconvenience of contacting us at this time.
